'''Good and Evil in''' '''''The Lord of the Rings''''' is an article by [[W.H. Auden]] discussing the theme of Good and Evil in [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s ''[[The Lord of the Rings]]''. It was published in ''Critical Quarterly'', Volume 10, Issue 1-2, [[1968]], pp. 138–142.

On [[28 September]], [[2007]], the article was published online by Blackwell Publishing Ltd.
